Introduction

Lucy is a South Korean rapper under H Music Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group WOOAH(formerly known as woo!ah!).

She made her debut as a member of WOOAH on May 15, 2020, with the group's first single album "Exclamation".

Lucy was a former child actress with experience in over 50 broadcasts, commercials, and pictorials. As a child, she filmed a commercial with famous Korean actor 'Cha Seung-Won'.
